<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_cfe0289eb931.aspx"><b>子衿</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsoncfe0289eb931">
<p>青青子衿，悠悠我心。纵我不往，子宁不嗣音？<br />青青子佩，悠悠我思。纵我不往，子宁不来？<br />挑兮达兮，在城阙兮。一日不见，如三月兮。</p>
